OL,3,CMan jailed for more than seven years
OL,4,Cfor raping two women
OL,6,FPolice Scotland say the conviction of
OL,7,Fa man for raping two women shows the
OL,8,Fforce is "determined to bring those
OL,9,Fresponsible to justice".
OL,11,FRicki Anderson, 37, was found guilty
OL,12,Fat Kilmarnock Sheriff Court on 21
OL,13,FFebruary, 2025 for the offences
OL,14,Fincluding rape, drugs supply and theft.
OL,16,FHe attacked a woman in a car between
OL,17,FEast Lothian and Dumfries in June
OL,18,F2021. She has since died.
OL,20,FHe attacked another woman in a flat in
OL,21,FDumfries in early 2022.
