OL,3,CMan jailed for more than seven years
OL,4,Cfor raping two women
OL,6,FAt the High Court in Glasgow on 23
OL,7,FApril 2025, Anderson was jailed for
OL,8,Fseven years and nine months, placed on
OL,9,Fthe sex offenders' register and given
OL,10,Fa 15-year non-harassment order.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Graeme Robertson
OL,13,Fof the Public Protection Unit at
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway Division said:
OL,15,F"Although one of the victims in this
OL,16,Fcase has passed away, it was right her
OL,17,Fevidence was heard in court through
OL,18,Fthe reading of statements.
