OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain with her family
OL,7,Fand the other victim, and I hope this
OL,8,Fsentencing offers them some comfort as
OL,9,Fthey move forward with their lives.
OL,11,F"I would also like to reassure our
OL,12,Fcommunities that we are committed to
OL,13,Finvestigating all reports of a sexual
OL,14,Foffence and we are determined to bring
OL,15,Fthose responsible to justice.
OL,17,F"I urge anyone who has been the victim
OL,18,Fof any offence of this nature to
OL,19,Fcontact us, where you will be fully
OL,20,Fsupported by our officers and partner
OL,21,Fagencies."
